title: Fortnite x TMNT Turtles Kick Baddie Butt Cinematic Short
description:
The Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles are back and kicking some baddie butt!

Leonardo, Donatello, Michelangelo, Raphael return to Fortnite. But this time they’ve brought their signature weapons with them. Don Leondardo's KATANAS, Michelangelo s NUNCHAKU, Donatello STAFF, or Raphael's SAI during this limited time event. 

Starting February 9, 2024. It’s Cowabunga, dudes! 

#fortnite #tmnt #gaming

title: Street Fighter 6 Ed Official Gameplay Trailer
description:
Ed, the troubled protégé will prove he's no longer a pawn when he enters Fighting Ground, World Tour, and the Battle Hub on February 27.

With psycho power imbued within, Ed pummels enemies with his mastery of boxing.
